{"tid":619382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戒人奶一年仍失敗 囝囝隨時扯衫超尷尬","createTime":"2018-04-06T14:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T15:52:31.000Z","uid":29627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"79407e6d6c459d94bef24237fe9f35178501adba","tid":619382,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"美國紐約22歲媽媽本克(Alicia Bencke)對她的2歲兒子凱登(Caiden)相當苦惱，因為她已經讓凱登戒人奶1年，但凱登依舊不時要求喝人奶，還不時對她扯衫，即使出門在外，凱登仍是會這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n本克表示，她大約從1年前開始，就要凱登戒人奶，凱登本來很快就適應改喝奶粉，沒想到就在這幾個月，凱登突然「反彈」，不時對媽媽說：「我要奶&hellip;&hellip;奶奶！」，甚至粗暴地扯本克的衣服，渴望喝到人奶。本克說，凱登不只在家這樣，就連在外面，只要想到就會做，讓她不知所措。<br />\n<br />\n本克還說，她帶著凱登逛超市時，凱登就會當眾對她扯衣，坦言「我真的很尷尬」。本克也說，當其他顧客看到這個場面，總是會大笑，如果遇到同樣身為媽媽的顧客，也都會給予會心的一笑，知道這是什麼樣的一個狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i5-NM4WWBW4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Di5-NM4WWBW4&d=v%2FFFyb0r89fiJAo8Co9bFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=dd2821be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i5-NM4WWBW4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180406/58039760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F58039760&d=v%2FFFyb0r89fiJAo8Co9bFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=13ef4a86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F58039760&h=a7715681\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180406/58039760</a>"},{"pid":"fdb49cb9a6fee19aeffc4919413bdcfa778a30ca","tid":619382,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f02bf62e9fa1aeedf3254208c93f67e3e49b2d99","tid":619382,"uid":19072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:50:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9664cf921861121f6dc64472c4db92384c3d23